(66, 40, 1, 'What is Shared Hosting?', '<p>Shared web hosting is an affordable hosting plan that&rsquo;s perfect for small businesses and start-ups. Multiple website owners share resources of a single server to make their sites available on the internet. WebSouls offers various shared hosting packages that are light on the wallet and can fulfil all your website needs. &nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 58, 1, '2020-03-12 05:57:07', '2020-05-06 06:18:44', NULL),
(67, 40, 1, 'Do I need to have prior technical knowledge for shared hosting?', '<p>No prior technical knowledge is required for shared hosting. Just after you&rsquo;ve ordered your service, we&rsquo;d send you your login details as well as all the necessary information required to start your hosting journey.&nbsp; In addition to this, we also offer quality support through live chat, email, and phone, so you can always hit us up in case of any questions.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 59, 1, '2020-03-12 05:57:21', '2020-05-20 11:21:57', NULL),
(68, 40, 1, 'How does shared hosting differ from business hosting?', '<p>The key difference between shared and businesses hosting is the number of clients per server. Apart from this, there are also certain limitations, such as the hourly emails. However, your website won&rsquo;t be affected in any other way if you decide to go for shared server space.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 60, 1, '2020-03-12 05:57:40', '2020-05-06 06:20:04', NULL),
