(118, 61, 1, 'Easy-to-Remember', '<p>It&rsquo;s great if your domain name includes a keyword to help with SEO, but make sure to keep it simple, catchy, and memorable. Avoid going for a name that&rsquo;s way too long or complicated.</p>', '1589788787.png', NULL, NULL, 110, 1, '2020-03-17 04:46:51', '2020-05-18 07:59:52', NULL),
(119, 61, 1, 'Resonates with Your Brand', '<p>Nothing is better than a domain name that&rsquo;s brandable, highly unique, and resonates with your business and company goals. Try and keep it relevant to the purpose of your website.</p>', '1589788799.png', NULL, NULL, 111, 1, '2020-03-17 04:48:28', '2020-05-18 08:00:13', NULL),
