(223, 119, 1, 'Easy-to-Remember', '<p>It&rsquo;s great if your domain name includes a keyword to help with SEO, but make sure to keep it simple, catchy, and memorable. Avoid going for a name that&rsquo;s way too long or complicated.</p>', '1589788651.png', NULL, NULL, 206, 1, '2020-04-27 11:58:38', '2020-05-18 07:57:33', NULL),
(224, 119, 1, 'Resonates with Your Brand', '<p>Nothing is better than a domain name that&rsquo;s brandable, highly unique, and resonates with your business and company goals. Try and keep it relevant to the purpose of your website.</p>', '1589788662.png', NULL, NULL, 207, 1, '2020-04-27 11:59:10', '2020-05-18 07:57:44', NULL),
