(399, 191, 1, 'Transfer .pk Domain', '<p>We know getting stuck can be terrible. So, to help you out, and to keep your site running smoothly, we&rsquo;re offering hassle-free domain name transfer without any charges at all.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to take on the web with us? Download our Domain Transfer Letter now and let us get you through!</p>', NULL, 'Transfer .pk Domain', 'first', 382, 1, '2020-04-29 08:19:18', '2020-05-06 10:15:44', NULL),
(400, 191, 1, 'Domain Renewals', '<p>Having your domain accidently expired can be a horrifying nightmare. We can help you stay on the World Wide Web, even if we aren&rsquo;t your current domain provider. Our magic wand is: we&rsquo;re the &ldquo;gold partners of .pk domains registry&rdquo;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So, are you stumbling? Grab our hand!</p>', NULL, 'Domain Renewals', 'secnd', 383, 1, '2020-04-29 08:20:18', '2020-05-06 10:16:23', NULL),
